# EduLens
## Preview

![Dashboard](assets/dashboard.png)
AI-powered student performance prediction system.

## Tech Stack
- FastAPI (Backend)
- React + Vite + Tailwind (Frontend)
- ML Model (SHAP explainability)

## Features
- Student risk prediction
- SHAP explanation
- AI chat assistant

## Run Locally
Backend:
uvicorn app.main:app --reload

Frontend:
npm run dev
